name: Real Nasty Icon Set
description:
Cover your kid's eyes. The infamous 'Nasty Icons' – created in 2014 as a fun side project – are back. 1px stroke on 30px grid. Fully editable strokes.


Send this file to a friend for a good laugh (and let us know if you managed to use it!)


This is an open-source project. We recommend using our Figma plugin to get access to all other free vector sets.
